oads/2025/02/fire-aid-billy-crystal@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/fire-aid-billy-crystal@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/fire-aid-billy-crystal@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/fire-aid-billy-crystal@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> FireAid宣布了收件人的首个5000万美元的赠款 - 在下面了解更多信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/la-music-community-tragic-wildfires-long-lasting-effects-3828259">洛杉矶音乐社区告诉我们有关野火的“悲惨”影响：“这将被感受多年”</a></strong></li></ul><p>上个月下半年，FireAid在洛杉矶<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/benefit-concert-for-victims-of-los-angeles-wildfires-announced-3828097">举办了两场同时的福利音乐会，</a>为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">今年早些时候毁灭性野火的受害者</a>筹集了资金。根据<a href="https://fireaidla.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方火灾组织的网站</a>，FireAid提出了超过1亿美元的大幅度估计。</p><p>宣布这笔1亿美元中的一半被搁置，以授予优先考虑“基于社区的组织，这些组织处于野火救济的前线”。昨天（2月18日），FireAID宣布获得了总筹集的总资金 - 每个接收者将根据其申请获得100,000美元或更多的收入，这些申请将用于立即救济。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGOMcJnPfVW/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><di