ies?</h2><p> <em>Boyhood&#39;s</em> Lee Sun-bin will star as Mi-gyeon, while Kang Tae-oh stars alongside her as Baek-ho. Notably, his appearance on the new K-drama will mark his first acting project since he was discharged from his military service in early 2024.</p><p> Other members of the show&#39;s supporting cast include <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/newtopia">Newtopia</a></em> and <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/decision-to-leave">Decision To Leave</a> &#39;s</em> Lee Hak-joo, <em>King The Land&#39;s</em> Kim Ga-eun, <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/han-river-police">Han River Police</a> &#39;s</em> Shin Hyun-seung, <em>Moon In The Day&#39;s</em> Jung Sin-hye and more.</p><h2> Is there a trailer for Netflix&#39;s <em>The Potato Lab</em> ?</h2><p> Netflix released the official trailer for the upcoming K-drama on February 18. The clip details the arrival of Baek-ho to the research centre as its latest director, his rigid attitude towards work and his initial friction with Mi-gyeong. Despite his rough start, he eventually warms up to Mi-gyeong and the rest of the team, and sparks fly. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="马铃薯实验室|官方预告片| Netflix [Eng Sub]" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/abDfjHG78vY?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h2> How to watch <em>The Potato Lab</em> ? </h2><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_tags tdi_87 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2" data-td-block-uid="tdi_87"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"> <em>The Potato Lab</em> will be premiering on March 1 via South Korean cable network tVN, thereafter airing new episodes every Saturday and Sunday at 9:20pm KST. The series will be simultaneously streamed on Netflix for international viewers.</div></div><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.