g its initial £20,000 target</a> – Mount said: “Anyone who has donated has made a massive difference, and I can&#39;t thank you enough from me and my family.我爱你们。”</p><p>本·“诗歌”山（Ben&#39;The Verse&#39;Mount）是钟摆的长期成员，首先加入澳大利亚鼓乐队（Australian Drum n&#39;Bass Band），作为他们的巡回演出，于2006年成为他们的巡回演出。2010年，他与乐队的正式录音首次亮相，并<a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/music-news/ben-verse-leaves-pendulum-8098330/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">与Pendulum在Pendulum中融为一体2018年初</a>专注于自己的职业。 </p><figure id="attachment_3787064" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3787064" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3787064" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/pendulum-Reading-AF@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/pendulum-Reading-AF@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/pendulum-Reading-AF@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/pendulum-Reading-AF@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/pendulum-Reading-AF@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/pendulum-Reading-AF@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/pendulum-Reading-AF@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3787064" class="wp-caption-text">钟摆执行Live AR阅读2024。</figcaption></figure><p> Pendulum are due to return to the UK for a collection of massive shows that will see them perform in Margate, Plymouth, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pendulum-announce-two-massive-uk-headline-shows-for-2025-3813687">Halifax, Scarborough</a> , and their biggest-ever show to date at Milton Keynes – <a href="https://pendulum.com/pages/tours" target="_blank" rel="noopener">you can get tickets to the shows, which will run between May and August, here</a> .</p><p> Last year, <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/reading-leeds-festival-2024-review-best-bits-liam-gallagher-lana-del-rey-fontaines-dc-3787423">Pendulum&#39;s set was named one of <em>NME</em> ’s Most Magical Moments of Reading &amp; Leeds 2024</a> . Shortly before their appearance at the iconic dual-festival, frontman <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pendulum-interview-napalm-new-album-bring-me-the-horizon-reading-leeds-3785482">Rob Swire spoke to <em>NME</em> about their recent comeback single &#39;Napalm&#39;</a> , which featured <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joey-valance">Joey Valance</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brae">Brae</a> .</p><p>他回想起该乐队的信号，他说：“我想把它重得多。我知道鼓&#39;n&#39;贝斯再次有片刻，我们不断让每个汤姆，迪克和哈利在我们的整个工作团队中都喜欢，&#39;你们必须加入这一点，开始制作一些适合Hedex的DNB。 ，但这只是我要他妈的的最后一件事。</p><p> “I feel most comfortable when we&#39;re in between worlds.一旦它太金属或太DNB，我就开始对此感到奇怪。该地面的中间是我们的理想区域。如果可以的话，我想把它重得多。”</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pendulums-ben-verse-shares-health-update-about-200-days-in-hospital-3839238">Pendulum&#39;s Ben Verse shares health update about 200 days in hospital</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
